# AgToosa Build Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-build` or any implementation work, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Build.md` precisely.

## Key constraints

- **Red before Green** — the failing test MUST exist before any implementation code is written.
- **Atomic tasks** — break the spec into the smallest independently testable units before coding.
- **No file > 500 lines** — refactor immediately if a file approaches the limit.
- Run SAST/DAST (Semgrep, CodeQL, Gitleaks) after each task, not just at the end.
- Update the task list in Linear and `Docs/Master-Plan.md` as tasks complete.
